# Claude — UI design only

Apply **only** when designing, styling, or refactoring visual UI for this Jekyll site.

## Do not apply when

- Editing `_config.yml`, post/content data, analytics, or build scripts
- Answering general questions unrelated to look and feel

## Source of truth

`design/design-system.md` — read before UI changes.

## Project knowledge (Claude Projects)

Upload to Project Knowledge:

1. `design/design-system.md`
2. `design/claude-project-knowledge.md` (condensed reference)

## Stack

SCSS (`_sass/`), HTML includes (`_includes/`, `_layouts/`), `index.html`. Map tokens to SCSS; match existing partials and skins.

## Hand-drawn essentials

- Wobbly multi-value `border-radius`; hard `4px 4px 0px` shadows (no blur)
- Colors: `#fdfbf7`, `#2d2d2d`, `#e5e0d8`, `#ff4d4d`, `#2d5da1`
- Fonts: Kalam + Patrick Hand; playful rotation; mobile-first with hidden desktop decorations
